{
  "stem": "26111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of that, if one takes the same percentage, let us say, of Jews in Germany to the Jewish population, that would be not far from 8%, as a matter of fact--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--7% or --7% Or 8%.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So if we take the same percentage, it would be-- seven times three-- about 20,000.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was probably somewhat more than that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would guess-- a very, very rough guess-- 20,000 to 30,000.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you must also remember that I knew a certain group of Jews, which was mainly the conservative ones or the non-religious ones, and in a certain class.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was also-- there were several Orthodox synagogues.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were also some Reformed synagogues.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so there may have been far, far more people than I-- than I was aware of.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was also a constant influx of Polish Jews even long before the German occupation-- the Germans marched into Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because Poles have not been particularly loving toward their Jews for quite a few years before Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so there were many that sought their fortunes and, and their-- and better treatment in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was not wealthy by-- his family was not a wealthy family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he had had a very successful and, I imagine, lucrative practice during quite a few years, certainly since the-- since the war, since the Second-- the First World War.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's what, 15 years or so, between say '18 and, and '33, actually, '36, so even more-- close to 20 years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I can only surmise that he had-- that he had some-- quite a bit of savings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What I can also vouch for is that not much-- very, very little remained at the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
